title: Big Apple
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Juice bar/cafe serves a large selection of juices and sandwiches (made with made-in-house wheat-free/yeast-free bread). There is one vegan sandwich on menu, but the staff will happily custom make something for you with ingredients such as hummus, avocado and many other veggies.
